### Introducing Autorun

////

////

~~~js
helloWorld = function() {
  alert(Session.get('message'));
}
~~~

////

////

////

~~~js
❯ Deps.autorun( function() { console.log('Value is: ' + Session.get('pageTitle')); } );
Value is: A brand new title
~~~
